properties.name: Birdwing butterfly 珠光鳳蝶
properties.description: Posted by MortBirdwing butterfly學 名： Troides magellanus (C. & R. Felder) 英 名： Birdwing butterfly 分 類： LEPIDOPTERA 鱗翅目 Papilionidae 鳳蝶科 形態描述： 大型鳳蝶，展翅1∼25公分，無尾狀突起；雄蝶 翅為黑色，前翅各翅脈外緣呈褐色，後翅金黃 色，各翅外緣線有鋸齒狀黑斑，反面與正面相 同；雌碟色較淡，後翅基部至中橫線間與亞外 緣各室有黃色斑。本種與黃裳鳳蝶十分相似， 但腹部背面呈黃褐色，不是黑色，且後赤金黃色 It is the biggest butterfly in Taiwan.

properties.name: Lyriothemis flava Oguma 樹穴蜻蜓
properties.description: Posted by Mort樹穴蜻蜓專以水桶和積水樹洞、竹筒為家，不喜其他水域環境。翅膀透明，端部褐色， 翅痣黑褐色。 成蟲,幼蟲愛吃孑孓也會吃蚊蟲，號稱蚊蟲殺手，1 年可繁殖3個世代，由於其特殊習性、外型和生殖方式，還被世界自然保育聯盟(IUCN)列為瀕臨滅絕的物種，全球主要分布在台灣、中國南部、日本、緬甸、印度、孟加拉等地。

properties.name: Pantala flavescens 薄翅蜻蜓
properties.description: Posted by Mort學校水池裡的蜻蜓 是台灣平地常見的蜻蜓,生活在平地都市至高山地區。稚蟲繁殖於各類靜水環境。秋季族群非常龐大，到處可見成群飛舞 The dragonfly in the school fish pond The pool son isn\'t big, having already grown some hydrophytes inside There have red dragonfly besides too.

properties.name: Siu Lek Yuen Hill 小瀝源山旁
properties.description: Posted by Kclama  Wing Dance on Vimeo Another Jumping Friend on Vimeo View this clip on Vimeo View this clip on Vimeo View this clip on Vimeo View this clip on Vimeo My home is located here, with high-rise buildings by the hill side. It is quite typical in Hong Kong because flat lands are very limited here. I really love this place with the convenience of all the shops near-by. And, at the same time, I can enjoy birding or bugging with a 5-10 min walks. In fact, I found more than 20 types of birds, more than 10 types of butterflies and many other little insects at the areas near-by. Enjoy the urban wildlife. :D Also, my other photos there.
